  "intent": "Execute Nextera DNA Flex NGS library cleanup protocol: Transfer 45\u00b5L supernatant from magnetic plate to fresh PCR plate, add 40\u00b5L nuclease-free water and 45\u00b5L sample purification beads (SPB) with 10x mixing at 100\u00b5L volume. Perform magnetic separation with 5-minute incubation, add 15\u00b5L additional SPB, then transfer 125\u00b5L supernatant to new plate with mixing. Execute two sequential 190\u00b5L ethanol washes with magnetic separation, air-dry for 5 minutes, then elute in 32\u00b5L resuspension buffer (RSB) with off-magnet mixing followed by 2-minute on-magnet incubation. Final transfer of 30\u00b5L eluate to clean plate.",
